TI  - Influence of Network forms on the internationalization process : A study on Swedish SMEs
PY  - 2012
T2  - KTH Publication Database DiVA (KTH Royal Institute of Technology)
DA  - 2012-01-01
AU  - Farooqi, Fahad
AU  - Miog, Robert
