TI  - Pure or Hybrid? The impact of business model design on SMEs internationalization performance
PY  - 2018
PB  - University of Siena
T2  - Use Siena air (University of Siena)
DA  - 2018-01-01
AU  - Casprini, Elena
AU  - Devigili, Matteo
